-a03309513dce\">&#x274c;</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"253\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"a15e3b11-bb7c-4496-bbdd-cbc61b5faf78\">Custom Payment Code (รหัสการชำระเงินแบบกำหนดเอง)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"278\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"529e9350-2caa-4d1b-af4c-84915a55848a\">N/A</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"253\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"d4fc461e-77d4-4e93-b6a4-95652e301b57\">Display Merchant Name (แสดงชื่อร้านค้า)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"278\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"e2ed9f33-d279-4ae7-bd91-b05c9a3790fd\">XENDIT</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"253\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"260ee695-3783-478d-b6ce-168812cf5235\">Display User Name (แสดงชื่อผู้ใช้)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"278\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"ff1eb546-d036-45be-a652-a5f3527306dd\">&#x274c;</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"253\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"ebe59eaf-3581-4b5e-9133-086846171bc3\">Set Expiry (กำหนดวันหมดอายุ)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"278\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"ad305fd9-8949-4702-bf15-52abc118017b\">&#x274c;</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"253\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"7750e331-7b15-4423-9ba5-f771994775fe\">Settlement Time (hours) (ระยะเวลาการชำระเงิน (ชั่วโมง))<