tyle=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"5c93e485-a74d-4a50-8a1b-9bba2a9f420b\">Compatible integration (การผสานการทำงานที่เข้ากันได้)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"278\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"7d30f1e6-c12f-4c51-943e-e601fe51191d\">Payment API, Payment Link</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><h2 data-block-id=\"2b081c08-ffd2-493a-b253-c4931f5f1c75\">ขั้นตอนการชำระเงิน</h2><p data-block-id=\"e10f7d87-26cd-4afd-b23e-3d7d291fbbbc\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/XZ4AarQDB9o\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" title style=\"display:flex;margin-right:auto;width:640px;height:360px;\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\"></iframe></p><p data-block-id=\"8e9aac87-b7ff-4f0e-b9c9-0178d8f76e42\"></p><p data-block-id=\"1fba7422-3f0f-475f-a3cd-ed72e33bce4f\"></p><p data-block-id=\"acd97665-43b1-498b-89ca-e66b24c0a68f\"></p><p data-block-id=\"490a489a-2a58-4dc9-96ea-9e5cc09fc8be\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Billease","Description":null},{"Code":"es-mx","Title":"Billease","Slug":"billease","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><p data-block-id=\"0ea65c3d-a38c-40be-a208-d546ab91ccec\"><img data-block-id=\"5d01eb56-8e21-4926-b400-9b83f10f326f\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/image-1735810846058.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt width=\"204\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link newtab style=\"width:204px;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"40d09386-139f-4cf1-8307-2c85d716974e\">BillEase es un servicio de compre ahora, pague después (BNPL) popular en Filipinas que permite a los clientes dividir sus compras en plazos. Ofrece opciones de pago flexibles, a menudo con cero interés, lo que hace que las compras en línea sean más accesibles para aquellos que quizás no tengan Credit Card o prefieran planes de pago a plazos.</p><hr class=\"hr-divider1\"><h2 data-block-id=\"6146dcc6-4245-4158-a034-de0971f8c50b\">Características</h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"531\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:531px;width:531px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:253px;\"><col style=\"width:278px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"253\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"db4dfef8-c563-4305-8c29-ef2b1aa63d40\">Código de Canal</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"278\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"fba8f786-e992-4e0c-8910-76d73b1ffdac\"><code>BILLEASE</code></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"253\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"05742465-0957-4c43-b4a1-a714d1ec5bd9\">Moneda</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"278\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"9f53d04c-d79c-4c69-902c-9b1f74789fef\">PHP</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"253\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"216547ce-9149-4c98-863b-af7a9b417559\">Monto Mínimo</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"278\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3p